<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Perkly 2.0</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <div class="glow"></div>
  <main class="layout">
    <header class="hero">
      <div class="badge">Version 2.0</div>
      <h1>Perkly</h1>
      <p class="lead">AI-powered credit card matching that cuts through the fine print.</p>
      <p class="sub">
        Tell us your category, spend, and preferences. We will surface the single card that
        best fits your lifestyle and income.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-meta">
        <div>
          <span>Focus</span>
          <strong>One best-fit card</strong>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span>Scope</span>
          <strong>No DBR or verification</strong>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span>Style</span>
          <strong>Fast, clear decisions</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="flow">
      <div class="progress">
        <div class="progress-bar" id="progressBar"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="step active" data-step="1">
        <h2>Let's start with your preferred card category.</h2>
        <p class="hint">Choose the lane you want your card to optimize for.</p>
        <div class="options" id="categoryOptions"></div>
        <div class="actions">
          <button class="btn primary" id="categoryNext" disabled>Continue</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-step="2">
        <h2>Pick a sub-category.</h2>
        <p class="hint">We only show the sub-categories that exist for your selection.</p>
        <div class="options" id="subcategoryOptions"></div>
        <div class="actions">
          <button class="btn ghost" data-back>Back</button>
          <button class="btn primary" id="subcategoryNext" disabled>Continue</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-step="3">
        <h2>Select a partner program.</h2>
        <p class="hint">If a card is tied to a partner, we will narrow it down here.</p>
        <div class="options" id="programOptions"></div>
        <div class="actions">
          <button class="btn ghost" data-back>Back</button>
          <button class="btn primary" id="programNext" disabled>Continue</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-step="4">
        <h2>Now tell us your monthly income.</h2>
        <p class="hint">
          For result accuracy, kindly ensure monthly income can be verified with payslips,
          salary certificates or other documentation.
        </p>
        <div class="input-row">
          <label for="income">Monthly income (AED)</label>
          <input type="number" id="income" min="0" placeholder="e.g. 30000" />
        </div>
        <div class="actions">
          <button class="btn ghost" data-back>Back</button>
          <button class="btn primary" id="incomeNext" disabled>Continue</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-step="5">
        <h2>Now give us an overview of your monthly spends.</h2>
        <p class="hint">
          Understanding your spending pattern allows us to recommend a card tailored to how
          you already spend, ensuring maximum return without changing your habits.
        </p>
        <div class="grid">
          <div class="input-row">
            <label for="spendTravel">Travel (Flights and Hotels)</label>
            <input type="number" id="spendTravel" min="0" placeholder="0" />
          </div>
          <div class="input-row">
            <label for="spendRetail">Retail (Online and Offline)</label>
            <input type="number" id="spendRetail" min="0" placeholder="0" />
          </div>
          <div class="input-row">
            <label for="spendUtilities">Utilities (Bills)</label>
            <input type="number" id="spendUtilities" min="0" placeholder="0" />
          </div>
          <div class="input-row">
            <label for="spendFood">Food and Groceries</label>
            <input type="number" id="spendFood" min="0" placeholder="0" />
          </div>
          <div class="input-row">
            <label for="spendFuel">Fuel</label>
            <input type="number" id="spendFuel" min="0" placeholder="0" />
          </div>
          <div class="input-row">
            <label for="spendTransport">Transportation</label>
            <input type="number" id="spendTransport" min="0" placeholder="0" />
          </div>
          <div class="input-row">
            <label for="spendRealEstate">Real Estate</label>
            <input type="number" id="spendRealEstate" min="0" placeholder="0" />
          </div>
          <div class="input-row">
            <label for="spendForeign">Foreign Spends (Monthly)</label>
            <input type="number" id="spendForeign" min="0" max="100000" placeholder="0" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="actions">
          <button class="btn ghost" data-back>Back</button>
          <button class="btn primary" id="spendNext">Continue</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-step="6">
        <h2>Before we recommend you a card, let's really customize this for you.</h2>
        <div class="card-block">
          <p class="label">Do you mind paying an annual fee if it would yield better card benefits?</p>
          <div class="radio-row">
            <label><input type="radio" name="annualFee" value="yes" checked /> I am okay with an annual fee</label>
            <label><input type="radio" name="annualFee" value="no" /> I prefer no annual fee</label>
          </div>
          <p class="hint">
            Cards with annual fees tend to offer more benefits. Our calculations will determine if
            it is worth it for you or not, we got you!
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-block">
          <p class="label">Any additional features you would like your card to have? (Pick up to 2)</p>
          <div class="options compact" id="featureOptions">
            <label class="chip"><input type="checkbox" value="Cinema Offers" /> Cinema Offers</label>
            <label class="chip"><input type="checkbox" value="Airport Lounge Access" /> Airport Lounge Access</label>
            <label class="chip"><input type="checkbox" value="Valet Parking" /> Valet Parking</label>
            <label class="chip"><input type="checkbox" value="Complementary Golf" /> Complementary Golf</label>
            <label class="chip"><input type="checkbox" value="Metal Card" /> Metal Card</label>
            <label class="chip"><input type="checkbox" value="Airport Transfers" /> Airport Transfers</label>
          </div>
          <p class="hint">
            We will try to match as many of these as possible; monetary value return will be prioritized.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="actions">
          <button class="btn ghost" data-back>Back</button>
          <button class="btn primary" id="extrasNext">Find my card</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-step="7">
        <h2>Your best-fit card</h2>
        <div id="result"></div>
        <div class="actions">
          <button class="btn ghost" data-back>Back</button>
          <button class="btn primary" id="restart">Start over</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script src="/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
